snippet.title: The Fall of the Dungeon Guardians   Gameplay Final #1
snippet.description:
Here a short gameplay video of the final version of The Fall of the Dungeon Guardians, a Dungeon Crawler for Windows / Mac / Linux.

More info : http://www.managames.com/DungeonGuardians/about/
Blog : http://www.managames.com/DungeonGuardians
IndieDB : http://www.indiedb.com/games/the-fall-of-the-dungeon-guardians

Note:
I'm playing without using Active Pause ( = press space to pause the game but still can enqueue orders), so it's more fun to watch ; to do so, I set a lower difficulty level than the one I'm usually playing with. But normally, in high difficulty levels, you'll have to use the Active Pause often.
